## Legend

- **id** `BKG-NNN` monotonic, never reused.
- **account** `@acct-<slug>` — the shared customer handle; optional (internal
  bookings omit it).
- **type** — from `.claude/schedule-gate.md`'s `booking_types` (default
  `general`).
- **start / end** — ISO 8601, timezone-qualified. Omit `end` for `all_day` or
  type-implied durations.
- **all_day** — `true` ⇒ `start`/`end` are dates only.
- **status** — `tentative | confirmed | done | cancelled`.
- **reminder** — absolute datetime, or an offset (`-1h`, `-1d`) against
  `start`. Intent only; the module does not deliver reminders.
